				\begin{document}$${\rm{DOX}}\,{\rm{loading}}\,{\rm{efficiency}}\,( \% )=\frac{{\rm{mS}}1({\rm{DOX}}\,{\rm{total}})-{\rm{m}}({\rm{DOX}}\,{\rm{in}}\,{\rm{supernatant}})}{{\rm{mS}}1({\rm{DOX}}\,{\rm{total}})}\times 100$$\end{document}DOXloadingefficiency(%)=mS1(DOXtotal)−m(DOXinsupernatant)mS1(DOXtotal)×100
